extendedInfo.description: Baby Doll Dance is fun activity/game for young Kids. Kids can simply press the buttons and Doll will start dancing. On press different buttons, doll will dance differently. She has different dances and songs. Its a very good time pass for young kids. This will keep kids occupied and busy. kids love this game. This game works beautifully on Tablets and Big Screens.Game Features:=============1) Baby Doll Dancing2) Touch the button to control the Multiple Dance Moves3) Multiple Dancing Sounds4) Multiple Cute Dancing Songs5) Special Support for Tablets and Big ScreensInstallation Info:==========Need Adobe Flash Player to Run. If Adobe Flash Player is not installed, then it will redirect to App Store for installing Adobe Flash Player. After installing it will work fine.Keywords:========Baby, Doll, Dance, Kids, Kid, Dolls, Dancing, Game, Fun, Child, ChildrenAds information:============In order to provide free game, we have put Ads. These banner ads will not disturb you.Bug Reporting:===========If you find any bugs, please report it to info@creativesoftwarestudio.comRatings & Improvement:=================Please rate us on Play Store and give your feedback to info@creativesoftwarestudio.com, so that we can improve it.Our Website:==========http://www.creativesoftwarestudio.com/games/Facebook Page:============http://www.facebook.com/pages/Creative-Software-Studio/398316796910914Twitter Page:=========https://twitter.com/css_appsPrivacy Policy==========http://www.creativesoftwarestudio.com/privacy/
